reinitialize
load ./outputs/2M5A_1/2M5A_csp.pdb, 2M5A_structure
hide everything, 2M5A_structure
show cartoon, 2M5A_structure
color cyan, 2M5A_structure and chain B
color gray30, 2M5A_structure and chain A
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 2
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 3
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 4
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 5
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 7
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 8
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 9
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 10
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 11
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 14
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 15
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 17
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 28
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 31
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 34
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 35
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 36
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 37
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 39
color red, 2M5A_structure and chain A and resi 44
set cartoon_transparency, 0.2, 2M5A_structure
# Color scheme:
# Ligand chain (B): cyan
# Receptor chain (A): gray30 (non-significant/no CSP), red (significant CSP via significant)
# Significant residues: 20
